 where* `d41d8cd98f00b204e9800998ecf8427e` - zone ID * `37cb64fe4a90adb5ca3afc04f2c82a2f` - zone lockdown ID as returned by [API](https://api.cloudflare.com/#zone-lockdown-list-lockdown-rules)

